information.title: Information
information.author: Developer of Sputnik Music
information.content:
Jared Simon R. Danao/Web-Developer H! I am Jared Simon R. Danao. 20 year of age, born on November 24, 2022. I currently live in Sitio Malilay II, Brgy. Matalaba, Santa Cruz, Marinduque.I studied in Marinduque State College in Tanza, Boac Marinduque, 2nd year student. I am taking Bachelor of Science Information Technology. My hobbies are playing basketball, playing online games like Mobile Legend, Call of Duty, Clash of Clan, riding motorcycle, watching anime, and adventure. I also love listening to musics because it makes comfortable and peace. Experienced web developer with a strong background in developing award-winning applications for a diverse clientele. 5+ years of industry experience includes programming, debugging, and wireframes. Received 80%+ experience scores on every web application built for SoftwareX.
Jemhar Jhon Logatoc/Web-Developer I'm jemhar jhon L. Logatoc, 19 years old from mahinhin, boac, marinduque. I studied elementary at mahinhin elementary svchool, then i tried to study in ilaya national high school but it is so hard so i decided to transfer in puting buhangin national high school. When i am in senior high school i take computer system servicing major. Currently I am taking bachelor of science in information technology at marinduque state college. I used to play basketball and mobiles games on my free time but it mostly consumed in playing basketball. I love to listen to the music so i wondered to create my own website to easily access my favorite songs. You may contact me on my social media account Facebook: Jemhar Logatoc,Gmail:jemharlandoylogatoc@gmail.com, also you can watch me on my YouTube channel but all of the videos out there is for activities only. Enhancing my knowledge in programming is my focus, perseverance is my investment, sucessful life is my goal'
